com.sun.java.xml.ns.javaee

Class HandlerType

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.java.xml.ns.javaee.HandlerType

  • public class HandlerType
extends Object
    Declares the handler for a port-component, service-ref. Handlers can access the init-param name/value pairs using the HandlerInfo interface. Used in: port-component, service-ref
